ens-for-summer-session/0000018f-91eb-d9a7-a9af-dbef8b8d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国国家安全顾问向内塔尼亚胡提出结束以色列加沙战争的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-national-security-adviser-presents-netanyahu-with-plans-to-end-israels-war-in-gaza/0000018f-9248-d9a7-a9af-db4e0a7d0000</link><description>拜登的高级顾问之一杰克·沙利文在与以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡和战时内阁部长本尼·甘茨的会晤中表达了美国和沙特关于结束战争的立场</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 20:38:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-national-security-adviser-presents-netanyahu-with-plans-to-end-israels-war-in-gaza/0000018f-9248-d9a7-a9af-db4e0a7d0000</guid></item><item><title>学生在哈佛和宾夕法尼亚大学亲巴勒斯坦抗议营地被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/students-arrested-at-harvard-and-upenn-pro-palestinian-protest-encampments/0000018f-9223-d212-abcf-d66fb96f0000</link><description>宾夕法尼亚大学的几名学生在试图占领校园建筑后等待重罪指控，而两名哈佛大学学生在新一波逮捕中被指控袭击和殴打</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 19:31:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/students-arrested-at-harvard-and-upenn-pro-palestinian-protest-encampments/0000018f-9223-d212-abcf-d66fb96f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列辛贝特安全部门邀请反内塔尼亚胡活动人士参加会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-shin-bet-security-service-brings-in-anti-netanyahu-activists-for-meeting/0000018f-91fa-d9d1-abcf-d7fefe0a0000</link><description>这些活动人士被召集到警察局参加“自愿会议”，消息人士称，这并不是为了威胁他们，而是为了“澄清法律界限”，并询问他们是否因抗议而受到威胁</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 19:20:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-shin-bet-security-service-brings-in-anti-netanyahu-activists-for-meeting/0000018f-91fa-d9d1-abcf-d7fefe0a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列侨民部长在马德里 Vox 会议上赞扬西班牙极右翼“与以色列结盟”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-minister-praises-spains-far-right-vox-for-aligning-with-israel/0000018f-91bd-d212-abcf-d7fdfe550000</link><description>以色列的阿米猜·奇克利与极右翼同行玛丽娜·勒庞、乔治亚·梅洛尼、维克多·欧尔班、哈维尔·米莱和 Vox 的圣地亚哥·阿巴斯卡尔一起宣称，加沙战争“是一场针对西方文明的未来、反对激进伊斯兰教的生死存亡之战”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 17:37:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-minister-praises-spains-far-right-vox-for-aligning-with-israel/0000018f-91bd-d212-abcf-d7fdfe550000</guid></item><item><title>“亲以色列”阴谋论者埃莉斯·斯特凡尼克来到以色列向特朗普求婚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-19/ty-article/.highlight/pro-israel-conspiracy-theorist-elise-stefanik-came-to-israel-to-court-trump/0000018f-91c4-d9a7-a9af-dbcef8a20000</link><description>与斯特凡尼克一样，绝大多数作为特朗普竞选搭档的潜在候选人公开出现的名字都倾向于全力支持以色列战争，同时攻击巴勒斯坦人和他们的支持者</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 17:30:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-19/ty-article/.highlight/pro-israel-conspiracy-theorist-elise-stefanik-came-to-israel-to-court-trump/0000018f-91c4-d9a7-a9af-dbcef8a20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和巴勒斯坦和平活动人士会见教皇，分享他们对共同未来的梦想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-palestinian-peace-activists-meet-pope-to-share-their-dream-of-a-shared-future/0000018f-9186-d212-abcf-d7efcfe30000</link><description>毛兹·伊农（Maoz Inon）的父母于 10 月 7 日被杀，阿齐兹·阿布·萨拉（Aziz Abu Sarah）在第二次起义中失去了弟弟，他们在 13,000 人面前向教皇方济各发表了讲话。教皇表示，他们的工作“不仅证明了对和平的渴望，而且是未来的计划”</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 16:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-palestinian-peace-activists-meet-pope-to-share-their-dream-of-a-shared-future/0000018f-9186-d212-abcf-d7efcfe30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 226 天：以色列国防军命令加沙北部拜特拉希亚居民撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-226-idf-orders-residents-in-north-gazas-beit-lahia-to-evacuate/0000018f-91b1-d9d1-abcf-d7fdbd860000</link><description>美国国家安全顾问沙利文正在以色列会见总理内塔尼亚胡和战时内阁部长甘茨 ■ 极右翼部长斯莫特里奇呼吁，如果真主党拒绝从边境撤军，以色列就占领加沙并入侵黎巴嫩南部 ■ 约旦外交部长呼吁调查此事他声称这是以色列在加沙战役期间犯下的战争罪 ■ 这是战争开始 226 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 16:35:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-226-idf-orders-residents-in-north-gazas-beit-lahia-to-evacuate/0000018f-91b1-d9d1-abcf-d7fdbd860000</guid></item><item><title>在取消和强烈抗议后，以色列耶路撒冷四重奏在阿姆斯特丹举行音乐会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/after-anti-israel-call-for-cancellation-jerusalem-quartet-plays-amsterdam-concert/0000018f-9110-d212-abcf-d77d8d9a0000</link><description>包括顶尖音乐家在内的超过 13,000 人签署了一份请愿书，呼吁阿姆斯特丹音乐厅允许耶路撒冷四重奏乐团进行演出，周六它也这样做了。音乐会和场外小型亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动顺利通过</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 15:56:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/after-anti-israel-call-for-cancellation-jerusalem-quartet-plays-amsterdam-concert/0000018f-9110-d212-abcf-d77d8d9a0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦消息人士明确表示，以色列支持的当地实体无法管理加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-sources-are-making-it-clear-that-no-israel-backed-local-entity-can-govern-gaza/0000018f-914b-d17a-a9df-915b5e5f0000</link><description>加沙的一位知名人士告诉《国土报》，“任何敢于执行这项任务的人都将是一名承包商，往好了说是无法承受压力，往坏了说是无法承受以色列的庇护”。然而，一项关于建立多国部队和外交进程的提议正在获得更多支持</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 15:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-sources-are-making-it-clear-that-no-israel-backed-local-entity-can-govern-gaza/0000018f-914b-d17a-a9df-915b5e5f0000</guid></item><item><title>按照这个速度，以色列活不过100岁生日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-this-rate-israel-wont-make-it-to-its-100th-birthday/0000018f-90cf-d065-a7ef-baff65310000</link><description>政府行政专家尤金·坎德尔和罗恩·祖尔在一篇新论文中警告说，一旦以色列精英看到各个“部落”无法就社会契约达成一致，他们就会逃离该国</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 14:15:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-this-rate-israel-wont-make-it-to-its-100th-birthday/0000018f-90cf-d065-a7ef-baff65310000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长斯莫特里奇呼吁占领加沙并接管黎巴嫩南部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-far-right-minister-smotrich-calls-to-occupy-gaza-take-over-south-lebanon/0000018f-90d7-d926-a18f-f5d7564d0000</link><description>贝扎莱·斯莫特里奇表示，只有在加沙地带永久存在才能阻止以色列南部的火箭弹。他说，应该向真主党发出最后通牒——从边境撤军，否则将面临以色列的入侵</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 12:42:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-far-right-minister-smotrich-calls-to-occupy-gaza-take-over-south-lebanon/0000018f-90d7-d926-a18f-f5d7564d0000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在加沙南部丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-southern-gaza/0000018f-90a8-d9a7-a9af-dbaec6520000</link><description>两名阵亡士兵被确认为 20 岁的纳赫曼·梅尔·海姆·瓦克宁中士和 20 岁的诺姆·比坦中士。第三名士兵加尔·沙巴特少校因上周在加沙战斗中受伤而死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 11:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-southern-gaza/0000018f-90a8-d9a7-a9af-dbaec6520000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日失去家人的以色列人遭到右翼抗议者袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-who-lost-his-family-on-october-7-assaulted-by-right-wing-protesters/0000018f-9074-d17a-a9df-9175244e0000</link><description>加迪·凯德姆 (Gadi Kedem) 在哈马斯袭击中失去了女儿、女婿和孙子，他向警方报案；本-格维尔部长称凯德姆是施暴者</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 11:15:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-who-lost-his-family-on-october-7-assaulted-by-right-wing-protesters/0000018f-9074-d17a-a9df-9175244e0000</guid></item><item><title>这位贝都因-以色列网球教练希望为她的社区实现更大的目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-05-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-bedouin-israeli-tennis-coach-wants-to-serve-a-bigger-purpose-for-her-community/0000018f-7c83-dd4f-ab8f-fdaf6a8f0000</link><description>26 岁的舒鲁克·斯瓦德·塞勒姆 (Shuruq Swaed Salem) 从未打过网球。 30 岁之前，她是一家独特的体育中心的副主任，该中心汇集了所有宗教信仰的以色列儿童</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 09:43:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-05-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-bedouin-israeli-tennis-coach-wants-to-serve-a-bigger-purpose-for-her-community/0000018f-7c83-dd4f-ab8f-fdaf6a8f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>